Sohu.Com to Buy Majority Stake in Online Game Firm 7Road for $101 Million

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-25T04:57:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/sohu-com-to-buy-majority-stake-in-online-game-firm-7road-for-101-million.html
Sohu.com Inc. (SOHU)  said its Changyou.com
subsidiary will pay as much as $101 million to buy a majority 
stake in online game company Shenzhen 7Road Technology Co.  Sohu said Changyou will acquire 68 percent of 7Road for a
cash payment of $68.26 million, and an additional cash payment
of as much as $32.76 million if a performance milestone is
reached, the Beijing-based company said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  